				<div id="post-692" class="hentry p2 post publish author-canuckaholic category-work-examples tag-britton-diamonds tag-website is-full comments-closed pings-open y2011 m08 d17 h11 alt slug-britton-diamonds"><h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://popdigital.ca/2011/08/17/britton-diamonds/" title="Permalink to Website: Britton Diamonds" rel="bookmark">Website: Britton Diamonds</a></h2>
<div class="entry-meta"><span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">By </span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://popdigital.ca/author/admin/" title="View all posts by Adrian">Adrian</a></span><span class="meta-sep meta-sep-entry-date"> | </span><span class="meta-prep meta-prep-entry-date">Published: </span><span class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2011-08-17T18:09:17-0700">August 17, 2011</abbr></span></div><!-- .entry-meta -->
					<div class="entry-content">
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-695" title="britton_diamonds" src="http://popdigital.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/britton_diamonds.jpg" alt="Britton Diamonds" width="558" height="531" /></p>
<h2>About:</h2>
<p>Britton Diamonds is a boutique diamond and jewellery retailer in downtown Vancouver. They were looking at refreshing their website and emphasizing the call-to-action of a visitor phoning or visiting their store. Pop Digital team members worked with Britton Diamonds to display sample inventory, much like an e-commerce storefront, and also created the ability for visitors to request a callback based on jewellery they found interested while browsing. The site also features a loose diamond inventory search application.</p>
<h2>Type of Project:</h2>
<p>Website. Underlying server architecture is LAMP. CMS is WordPress.</p>
<h2>URL:</h2>
<p><a title="Britton Diamonds" href="http://brittondiamonds.com/" target="_blank">brittondiamonds.com</a></p>
<h2>What We Did:</h2>
<div class="column">
<ul>
<li>HTML/XHTML</li>
<li>CSS</li>
<li>PHP</li>
<li>Javascript</li>
<li>jQuery</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="column">
<ul>
<li>Graphic Design</li>
<li>Database</li>
<li>WordPress</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="clearFloats"></div>
