				<div id="post-636" class="hentry p5 post publish author-canuckaholic category-work-examples tag-golf tag-northlands tag-website is-full comments-closed pings-closed y2011 m07 d04 h11 slug-northlands-golf-course"><h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://popdigital.ca/2011/07/04/northlands-golf-course/" title="Permalink to Website: Northlands Golf Course" rel="bookmark">Website: Northlands Golf Course</a></h2>
<div class="entry-meta"><span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">By </span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://popdigital.ca/author/admin/" title="View all posts by Adrian">Adrian</a></span><span class="meta-sep meta-sep-entry-date"> | </span><span class="meta-prep meta-prep-entry-date">Published: </span><span class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2011-07-04T18:00:35-0700">July 4, 2011</abbr></span></div><!-- .entry-meta -->
					<div class="entry-content">
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-637" title="Northlands Golf Course" src="http://popdigital.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/07/northlands_screen_558x300.jpg" alt="Northlands Golf Course" width="558" height="300" /></p>
<h2>About:</h2>
<p>Northlands opened for 18 hole public play in 1997 and has earned the reputation of being Metro Vancouver’s Premiere Public Course. Located in North Vancouver, Northlands presents a well formulated mix of challenging holes, friendly scenic downhill vistas and strategically located natural hazards.</p>
<h2>Type of Project:</h2>
<p>Website. Underlying server architecture is LAMP. CMS is WordPress.</p>
<h2>URL:</h2>
<p><a title="Northlands Golf Course" href="http://golfnorthlands.com" target="_blank">golfnorthlands.com</a></p>
<h2>What We Did:</h2>
<div class="column">
<ul>
<li>HTML/XHTML</li>
<li>CSS</li>
<li>PHP</li>
<li>Javascript</li>
<li>jQuery</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="column">
<ul>
<li>Graphic Design</li>
<li>Database</li>
<li>WordPress</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="clearFloats"></div>
