				<div id="post-627" class="hentry p7 post publish author-canuckaholic category-user-experience-design-2 untagged is-full comments-closed pings-closed y2011 m06 d09 h06 slug-animated-tribute-to-ux-design"><h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://popdigital.ca/2011/06/09/animated-tribute-to-ux-design/" title="Permalink to Animated Tribute to UX Design" rel="bookmark">Animated Tribute to UX Design</a></h2>
<div class="entry-meta"><span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">By </span><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://popdigital.ca/author/admin/" title="View all posts by Adrian">Adrian</a></span><span class="meta-sep meta-sep-entry-date"> | </span><span class="meta-prep meta-prep-entry-date">Published: </span><span class="entry-date"><abbr class="published" title="2011-06-09T13:25:07-0700">June 9, 2011</abbr></span></div><!-- .entry-meta -->
					<div class="entry-content">
<p><img class="alignright size-full wp-image-628" title="ux_design_animation" src="http://popdigital.ca/wp-content/uploads/2011/06/ux_design_animation.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="169" />An enjoyable animated cartoon for UX designers, and anyone who loves them.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.uxmag.com/short-news/an-animated-tribute-to-ux-design" target="_blank">Part 1</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.uxmag.com/short-news/animated-tribute-to-ux-design-part-2" target="_blank">Part 2</a></p>
<div class="selfclear">&nbsp;</div>
<div class="tweetthis" style="text-align:right;"><p> <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="tt" href="http://twitter.com/share?url=http://popdigital.ca/2011/06/09/animated-tribute-to-ux-design/&text=Animated+Tribute+to+UX+Design&via=tweetthisplugin&related=richardxthripp%2Ctweetthisplugin" title="Post to Twitter"><img class="nothumb" src="http://popdigital.ca/wp-content/plugins/tweet-this/icons/en/twitter/tt-twitter6.png" alt="Post to Twitter" /></a></p></div>
										</div><!-- .entry-content -->
					<div class="entry-utility"><span class="cat-links">Posted in <a href="http://popdigital.ca/category/user-experience-design-2/" title="View all posts in User-Experience Design" rel="category tag">User-Experience Design</a></span> <span class="meta-sep meta-sep-tag-links">|</span> <span class="comments-link comments-closed-link">Comments closed</span></div><!-- .entry-utility -->
